The Russian Embassy in China and the Russian Cultural Center in Beijing jointly organizes the event in Beijing on September 4, commemorating the end of WWII and the 74th anniversary of the victory of the Chinese People's War of Resistance against Japanese Aggression (1931-45). Dmitrii Lukiantsev, Charge d 'affaires of the Russian Embassy participated in the event and gave an opening speech. Photo: Yin Yeping/GT 
